<div class="dialog">  
  <div class="header">
    <h2><%= t("winnow.general.no_script_message") %></h2>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <p>Winnow requires a browser feature called JavaScript. All modern browsers support JavaScript. You probably just need to change a setting in order to turn it on.</p>

    <p>Please see: <%= link_to "How to enable JavaScript in your browser.", "http://www.google.com/support/bin/answer.py?answer=23852", :target => "_blank" %></p>

    <p>If you use ad-blocking software, it may require you to allow JavaScript from <b><%= request.host %></b>.</p>

    <p>Once you've enabled JavaScript you can <%= link_to "try loading this page again", url_for(params) %>.</p>

    <p>Thank you.</p>
  </div>
</div>
